data.label: 百川 SDK
data.description: 百川云推送是基于大数据的阿里移动云服务，实现更快、更稳、更准的实时推送。旨在为百川移动应用提供从云端到移动终端的优质的信息推送服务。开发者只需通过简单的配置和编码工作，即能够快速搭建起服务于自身业务的、高效稳定的推送服务。

data.label: 百川 SDK
data.description: Baichuan Cloud Push is an Alibaba Mobile Cloud service based on big data, achieving faster, more stable, and more accurate real-time push. It aims to provide high-quality information push services from the cloud to mobile terminals for Baichuan mobile applications. Developers can quickly build efficient and stable push services for their own business through simple configuration and coding work.
